  "text": "Statistical analysis. Survival probabilities over time were determined by the Kaplan-Meier method [CITATION_1] . The effect of each prognostic variable was analyzed using the log-rank test. The analyses were performed using SPSS statistics version 17.0 software (SPSS Inc., Chicago, IL, USA). Differences in functional outcome between groups were analyzed by the Mann-Whitney U-test. P<0.05 was considered to be statistically significant.",
